text: Heinz Franke (born 4 August 1928) is a German former sports shooter. He competed in the 25 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:Possibly living people Category:German male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of the United Team of Germany Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Wurzen
